# 🕒 Stopwatch Timer App

This is a simple **stopwatch timer app** built with **Streamlit**. It allows users to start, stop, and reset a timer with an easy-to-use web interface.

## 🚀 Features

- **Start** the stopwatch
- **Stop** the stopwatch
- **Reset** the stopwatch
- Displays the **elapsed time** in seconds

## 🛠️ Requirements

- **Python 3.x**
- **Streamlit**

## 📦 Installation

1. **Clone the Repository**

   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/your-repository.git
   cd your-repository
